snippet.title: Decay of Logos - Now available for wishlisting on Steam!
snippet.description:
Our first Unity game is finally available for wishlisting on Steam! 
Learn more: https://store.steampowered.com/app/759570  
Making full use of our Unity products, it will be available later on this year for PC, Xbox One, PS4, and Switch. Wishlist today to be notified of all updates!
More about our Unity Products: https://tinyurl.com/y3jcaqet
